log-entry.text: Ship wreckage, seemingly belonging to the freighter commanded by Dal Busta, was found close to his last known location. It is possible that the Scale Plate Pact would have attempted to silence him and his crew before taking further hostile actions against the Hatikvah Free League.[\012][\012]There was no clear evidence of escape pods being launched, nor any report of distress calls in the area.
